INSERT INTO
                via_btc_inscriptions_request_history (
                    commit_tx_id,
                    reveal_tx_id,
                    inscription_request_id,
                    inscription_request_context_id,
                    signed_raw_tx,
                    actual_fees,
                    sent_at_block,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, NOW(), NOW())
            RETURNING
                id
